Unsorted TODO list for pgpry
============================

Things to do be done for 0.1: 
   - Add support for state saving and reloading the guesser state
   - Add option listing for specific guessers
   - Add prefix and suffix filter (is not efficient via regular expresssions)
   - Tests:
     - Add more bevhaviour tests (help screen, version screen, failure handling etc.) 
     - Add compiled tests for program components, i.e. the Memblock class 
   - Make a small web page

Future work:
 - Add support for saving key data unencrypted
 - Add networking support
 - Add missing algorithms: DES, Triple-DES and Twofish, MD5, RIPE-MD, SHA >= 256
